On 7/4/2012 3:15 PM, C. Dreike wrote:
> Hi Collective,
> Can anyone recommend wide band O2 read out system? ie sensor, cable
> and digital dashboard gage?
> Also thinking about a head temp gage. (Dakota Digital maybe?)

LC-1 for the WBO2:

http://www.innovatemotorsports.com/products/lc1.php

In addition to the LC-1, you'll need to pick a gauge that you like.  And 
for the CHT, you'll wanna go with Dakota Digital:

http://www.dakotadigital.com/index.cfm/page/ptype=product/product_id=348/category_id=248/home_id=59/mode=prod/prd348.htm

And then you'll want to get the sender with the 18' wire.


The above items aren't cheap, but they work, and they're accurate.

Mike
